snippet.title: Dave.EXE: Punchies, Paddles, Propaganda | Update #2 OUT NOW!!!
snippet.description:
Dave.EXE's massive new update is out! Take on quests from the local Berry the Bears, brand new cosmetics to unlock, items to acquire at the blacksmith, new locations to explore, dangerous foes to encounter and more! All in the newest update for Dave.EXE, only available on Patreon.


Special thanks to Padre Snowmizzle for making the trailer ► https://twitter.com/PadreSnowmizzle
And a big thank you to Josh J. Olmos Jr for narrating this video ► https://twitter.com/PracticallyJosh
